body.raw:
Bringing simple easy iframe embeddings with the new Embed tag

```mdx
<Embed
    src="logwatch.vercel.app/widget"
    className="h-full w-full rounded-2xl"
/>
```

## Embed Example

<Embed
    src="/widget"
    className="h-full w-full rounded-2xl"
/>
